nlc config - Manage configuration

[1mUsage:[0m
  nlc config COMMAND
  nlc config [COMMAND] --help | -h

[1mCommands:[0m
  [32mshow[0m    Show configuration and environment
  [32mclear[0m   Delete the config file (falling back to default values)
  [32medit[0m    Edit the configuration file (create it first if needed)
  [32mnew[0m     Create a new config file
